\id DEU Matupi Chin Standard Bible (MCSB)
\h OLKHUENG RHAEPNAH
\toc1 Olkhueng Rhaepnah
\toc2 Olrhaepnah
\toc3 Olr
\mt1 OLKHUENG RHAEPNAH
\mt2 (Deuteronomy)
\is1 Olkhueng Rhaepnah Cabu Kawng
\ip \sc Olkhueng Rhaepnah\sc* \it (Deuteronomy)\it* cabu he Hebru dongah tah \it “The Pentateuch”\it* (Cabu Panga) ti lamkhaw \it “Torah”\it* (Olkhueng) tilam khaw a thui. Pathen loh amah olkhueng \it (Law)\it* he Sunglatnah \it (Exodus)\it*neh Thotuengnah \it (Leviticus)\it* cabu dongah Moses taengah a uen. Te dongah he kah cabu he \sc Olkhueng \it (Nomy)\it* Rhaepnah \it (Deutero)\it* \sc* tila a ming paek la om. Tahae kah \sc Olkhueng Rhaepnah\sc* cabu dongah tah Moses loh pilnam taengah patoeng a thui pah kawng te a tueng sak. He cabu dongah Pathen hlang rhoek loh uempomnah neh khosaknah khaw, Pathen kah daemnah kawng, Pathen kah a saii so ah pilnam loh omngaih ham a kueknah kawg a thui. Hmailong kah cadil cahna long khaw Boeipa kah moi neh paipi dongah uepom la khosak ham khaw pahoi a uen.
